article.description: Tanner Krebs had 19 points and six rebounds and Dan Fotu posted 13 points as Saint Mary's topped Loyola Marymount 73-62 on Saturday night.
article.headline: Krebs lifts Saint Mary's (Cal) over Loyola Marymount 73-62
article.linkText: Krebs lifts Saint Mary's (Cal) over Loyola Marymount 73-62
article.story: LOS ANGELES -- Tanner Krebs had 19 points and six rebounds and Dan Fotu posted 13 points as Saint Mary's topped Loyola Marymount 73-62 on Saturday night. Jordan Ford had 12 points for Saint Mary's (18-4, 5-2 West Coast Conference). Malik Fitts added 11 points. Eli Scott had 18 points for the Lions (8-13, 2-5). Jordan Bell added 14 points. Saint Mary's plays Portland at home on Thursday. Loyola Marymount faces Pacific on the road on Thursday. --- For more AP college basketball coverage: https://apnews.com/Collegebasketball and http://twitter.com/AP-Top25 --- This was generated by Automated Insights, http://www.automatedinsights.com/ap, using data from STATS LLC, https://www.stats.com
